ent run that coincided with the country's talent flooding theNBA.\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9993023313695661, \"rank\": 0.000696051802145483, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fern\\u00e1ndez is now the coach, after replacing Nick Nurse, who replaced Triano.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 475, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.191128855719803e-28, \"text\": \"Fern\\u00e1ndez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\"}, {\"begin\": 519, \"end\": 529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Nurse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nick Nurse\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Nurse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Nurse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nurse is not in charge only because he could not find a way to manage switching professional jobs while keeping the gig withCanadalast summer.\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Canada Basketball hired Fern\\u00e1ndez to replace him.\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 695, \"end\": 712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.103866876093917e-16, \"text\": \"Canada Basketball\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.191128855719803e-28, \"text\": \"Fern\\u00e1ndez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fern\\u00e1ndez and Triano are on Mike Brown's staff with the Kings.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 745, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.191128855719803e-28, \"text\": \"Fern\\u00e1ndez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\"}, {\"begin\": 773, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_E._Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.177430602757549e-16, \"text\": \"Mike Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_E._Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_E._Brown\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Again, eerie stuff, even if the basketball world is smaller than you think.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  Somewhere in the back of Triano's mind, he must be thinking that it would have been nice to be able to speak as confidently - with truth - when he was the head coach as Fern\\u00e1ndez is now.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 1086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1069, \"end\": 1078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.191128855719803e-28, \"text\": \"Fern\\u00e1ndez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe we can get to No.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 in the rankings.\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And not just get there but sustain it,\\\" Fern\\u00e1ndez said before his Kings eviscerated what's left of theToronto Raptors123-89 on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1177, \"end\": 1186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.191128855719803e-28, \"text\": \"Fern\\u00e1ndez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's amazing what one bronze medal at the World Cup andthe first spot in the Olympicsfor the men in the past six cycles will do.\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a reason for Canada to be excited.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1427, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.828588761930053, \"rank\": 0.20503511858170032, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tuesday, Fern\\u00e1ndez learned his team will be in a group with fifth-ranked Australia and the winners of the last-chance qualifying tournaments in Spain and Greece.\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1458, \"end\": 1467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.191128855719803e-28, \"text\": \"Fern\\u00e1ndez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\"}, {\"begin\": 1522, \"end\": 1531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.8566542983236399, \"rank\": 0.1215439805734386, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1593, \"end\": 1598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999998681233, \"rank\": 1.3184260618148927e-10, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1603, \"end\": 1609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999912197381, \"rank\": 8.78007406490031e-09, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The hosts and Slovenia are the two favourites to come out of the latter tournament, and Spain - Fern\\u00e1ndez's home country and his FIBA touchstone - is strongly favoured to get out of the tournament it will host.\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1625, \"end\": 1633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999856058822, \"rank\": 1.432994191062218e-08, \"text\": \"Slovenia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These are theOlympics, so there is no such thing as an easy draw.\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, Fern\\u00e1ndez can afford to be optimistic.\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1896, \"end\": 1905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.191128855719803e-28, \"text\": \"Fern\\u00e1ndez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the group of players that (general manager) Rowan (Barrett) put together was amazing.\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1989, \"end\": 1994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowan_University\", \"score\": 0.9998843230459321, \"rank\": 9.033563215523442e-05, \"text\": \"Rowan\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowan_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowan_University\"}, {\"begin\": 1996, \"end\": 2003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RJ_Barrett\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 5.8464086642308015e-12, \"text\": \"Barrett\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RJ_Barrett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RJ_Barrett\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end of the day, that's what you need.\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You need the horses, and we do have that,\\\" Fern\\u00e1ndez said.\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2119, \"end\": 2128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.191128855719803e-28, \"text\": \"Fern\\u00e1ndez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Moving forward, we are going to have the opportunity to improve the team.\\\"\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That will be the focus of the next few months, leading up to training camp in Toronto about a week after the NBA Finals is scheduled to end.\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2290, \"end\": 2297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto_Raptors\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4674726919908892e-20, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto_Raptors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto_Raptors\"}, {\"begin\": 2321, \"end\": 2331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\", \"score\": 0.9999999987558112, \"rank\": 6.301737392318318e-10, \"text\": \"NBA Finals\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barring injuries or other unexpected developments, seven no-doubters will be in France for Canada: MVP candidateShai Gilgeous-Alexander,Luguentz Dort,RJ Barrett,Kelly Olynyk,Nickeil Alexander-Walker,Dwight PowellandDillon Brooks.\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2433, \"end\": 2439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999705255509, \"rank\": 2.815952055205139e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2444, \"end\": 2450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.828588761930053, \"rank\": 0.20503511858170032, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Can