 playoff run, he will be there.\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2612, \"end\": 2618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.828588761930053, \"rank\": 0.20503511858170032, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"International stalwart Melvin Ejim is another likely member of the squad.\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2763, \"end\": 2774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melvin_Ejim\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Melvin Ejim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melvin_Ejim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melvin_Ejim\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  After that, it's anybody's guess.\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2863, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Three summers ago, the program asked for a three-summer commitment from its players to build the chemistry that has been absent from some of the most recent Canadian teams, but Barrett and his team have already had to go beyond thatoriginal list of 14.\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 3116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3021, \"end\": 3029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9993023313695661, \"rank\": 0.000696051802145483, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 3041, \"end\": 3048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RJ_Barrett\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 5.8464086642308015e-12, \"text\": \"Barrett\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RJ_Barrett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RJ_Barrett\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Fern\\u00e1ndez referenced, there are certain players not among that group who could really help.\", \"from\": 3117, \"to\": 3211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3120, \"end\": 3129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.191128855719803e-28, \"text\": \"Fern\\u00e1ndez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luis_Fernandez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Canada could certainly use a mobile centre with size to deal withVictor Wembanyama,Giannis Antetokounmpo(if Greece makes it),Nikola Joki\\u0107and whoever the United States has up front, but that sort of player does not exist.Andrew Nembhardof theIndiana Pacers, however, would help as the type of backup guard who was lacking on last summer's team.\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3213, \"end\": 3219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.828588761930053, \"rank\": 0.20503511858170032, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3296, \"end\": 3317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giannis_Antetokounmpo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giannis Antetokounmpo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giannis_Antetokounmpo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giannis_Antetokounmpo\"}, {\"begin\": 3321, \"end\": 3327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999912197381, \"rank\": 8.78007406490031e-09, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"htt